{"tid":618576,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"保險代理被炒竟要倒賠14萬獎金 上千保單變「孤兒單」","createTime":"2018-04-06T02:27:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T02:33:45.000Z","uid":119507,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8d9c34f8f9850298dd0e50e6f0ec37a1ee4041d3","tid":618576,"uid":119507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:27:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180406/58037950\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180406%2F58037950&d=BqGjCycW4fN3prVCEleS%2FlKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=8d4083c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180406%2F58037950&h=5d785710\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180406/58037950</a><br />\n<br />\n「公司炒人仲要人賠錢畀公司？」中國人壽（海外）被指去年底起與未完約的保險代理終止合約，消息指涉及約1,000人。代理除失去工作，更被追討已發放的培訓費、獎金及津貼等，工會接獲其中70名代理求助，各人被追款項由6,000元至14萬元不等，總額350萬元。工會批評中國人壽賺了客戶，還要剝削代理的報酬，已去信該公司要求撤回追討。<br />\n<br />\n曾女士於2016年11月經鄰居介紹，投身保險業，與中國人壽（海外）簽下2年合約，「個經理仲話做一蚊（佣金收入），佢哋就畀一蚊津貼（獎金）我。我覺得咁幾好，努力完仲有獎勵」。當時上線經理僅稱合約期內「跳槽」要退回獎金，「冇講過炒咗要嘔番出嚟」。<br />\n<br />\n曾女士在朋友幫助下，簽成了20多張單，但今年3月8日卻收到公司通知要終止合約，並向她追討10多萬元津貼和獎金。事後除了家人有怨言，幫她買保險的朋友亦不滿保單成「孤兒單」。她希望中國人壽停止追討，並讓她復職。"},{"pid":"36ca7af0a878ce12f83ebf327829cee5649697b8","tid":618576,"uid":3647,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:29:27.000Z","msg":"班保險佬有冇幫自己份工買保險"},{"pid":"245333e29b43458a2d3b03e5f47d9bce4ceafe0a","tid":618576,"uid":4564,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"36ca7af0a878ce12f83ebf327829cee5649697b8","tid":618576,"uid":3647,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:29:27.000Z","msg":"班保險佬有冇幫自己份工買保險"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:32:10.000Z","msg":"「如果佢有買到XX保，就唔洗擔心依家啦」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96aaf1a06cb8f53f7b3fde9ca7ff8364a5c33917","tid":618576,"uid":120908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:33:45.000Z","msg":"曾女士在朋友幫助下，簽成了20多張單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}